The '''1970–71 Kentucky Wildcats men's basketball team''' was head coach [[Adolph Rupp]]'s second to last team. While not as successful as his past Wildcats teams, would go reach the Elite Eight, finishing the season with a 22-6 record (16-2) and a [[Southeastern Conference]] regular season championship.

